file: crates/ctx-core/Cargo.toml
behavior: Defines the ctx-core crate: a dependency-free library providing shared primitives and the canonical access-gate logic (secret/binary/gitignored deny) used by other crates.
edit_notes:
  - Crate is intentionally kept dependency-free; adding a dependency here contradicts the package description and propagates to all dependents.
  - This crate is documented as the single source of truth for the security-sensitive access gate; gate logic should not be reimplemented elsewhere in the workspace.
  - Inherits lint settings from [workspace] lints rather than defining its own.
functions:
invariants:
  - No entries under [dependencies]; the crate must build with zero external crates.
external_deps: